    {
      "num": 36,
      "text": "During an ISO 27001:2022 implementation audit, you discover that the organization's risk assessment process does not explicitly document the interdependencies between information assets and business processes. According to ISO/IEC 27001:2022 Clause 6.1.2, what is the PRIMARY consequence of this omission?",
