      "justification_wrong": "Options B and C misrepresent ISO requirements. Option D introduces non-existent ISO approval processes. Effective classification requires collaborative governance with defined responsibilities per control 5.2 (Information security roles and responsibilities)."
    },
    {
      "num": 38,
      "text": "During the design phase of ISO 27001:2022 implementation, you identify that the organization's access control matrix (control 5.3) does not address temporary privileged access for emergency system maintenance. How should this be managed per ISO/IEC 27002:2022 principles?",
      "tag": "Technological Controls - Access Management",
      "options": [
        "C. Allow unrestricted emergency access provided the CISO is notified afterward by email",
