      "justification_correct": "ISO/IEC 27002:2022 Clause 6.6 mandates segregation between development, testing, and production environments. Developers with production admin credentials create conflict of interest, audit trail contamination, and unauthorized change risk. Formal access requests with approval separation required.",
      "justification_wrong": "Option B ignores control intent. Option C creates operational dysfunction. Option D provides no segregation. Production administrative access requires distinct approval workflows from development roles per control 8.2 (Privileged access rights) requirements."
