      "text": "During ISO 27001:2022 lead implementation, you're reviewing the organization's incident response plan (control 8.16). The plan states: 'All security incidents are classified by the IT Department within 2 hours.' What SIGNIFICANT gap exists in alignment with ISO/IEC 27002:2022 Clause 8.16?",
