      "justification_correct": "ISO 27001:2022 Clause 7.2 (Competence) and 7.3 (Awareness) mandate documented competency and awareness programs. ISO 27002:2022 A.6.2 (Information security awareness) and A.6.3 (Information security training) require structured, monitored programs. Clause 9.1 requires performance evaluation of all controls, including people-dependent ones.",
